<tmc-service-paragraph><pub id="RM25T0E"><servcat id="_51"><name>Engine / Hybrid System</name><section id="_029760"><name>1VD-FTV ENGINE CONTROL</name><ttl id="_0135360"><name>ECD SYSTEM</name><para category="J" id="RM1000000017AMI"><dtccode/><dtcname>MIL Circuit</dtcname><subpara category="03" id="RM1000000017AMI_01"><name>DESCRIPTION</name><content5><topic><title>for RHD</title><ptxt>The MIL (Malfunction Indicator Lamp) is used to indicate vehicle malfunction detections by the ECM. When the ignition switch is turned to ON, power is supplied to the MIL circuit, and the ECM provides the circuit ground which illuminates the MIL.</ptxt><ptxt>The Malfunction Indicator Lamp (MIL) is used to indicate vehicle malfunctions detected by the ECM.The MIL operation can be checked visually. When the ignition switch is first turned to ON, the MIL shouldbe illuminated and should then turn off after the engine is started. If the MIL remains illuminated or is notilluminated, conduct the following troubleshooting procedure using the GTS.</ptxt></topic><topic><title>for LHD</title><ptxt>The Malfunction Indicator Lamp (MIL) is used to indicate vehicle malfunctions detected by the ECM.The MIL operation can be checked visually. When the ignition switch is first turned to ON, the MIL shouldbe illuminated and should then turn off after the engine is started. If the MIL remains illuminated or is notilluminated, conduct the following troubleshooting procedure using the GTS.</ptxt></topic></content5></subpara><subpara category="03" id="RM1000000017AMI_02"><name>WIRING DIAGRAM</name><content5><figure translate="E" type="1"><title>for RHD</title><graphic graphicname="A182518E16" height="3.812598425in" width="7.168479331in"/></figure><figure translate="E" type="1"><title>for LHD</title><graphic graphicname="A403501E01" height="3.812598425in" width="7.168479331in"/></figure></content5></subpara><subpara category="01" id="RM1000000017AMI_06"><name>PROCEDURE</name><testgrp cellposition="1-1" id="RM1000000017AMI_06_0001"><testtitle>CHECK THAT MIL IS ILLUMINATED</testtitle><content6><test1><ptxt>Check the illumination condition of the MIL.</ptxt></test1><spec type="other"><title>Result</title><table pgwide="1"><tgroup cols="3"><colspec colname="col1" colwidth="2.34in"/><colspec colname="col2" colwidth="2.34in"/><colspec colname="col3" colwidth="2.40in"/><thead><row><entry align="center" valign="middle"><ptxt>MIL</ptxt></entry><entry align="center" valign="middle"><ptxt>Condition</ptxt></entry><entry align="center" valign="middle"><ptxt>Proceed to</ptxt></entry></row></thead><tbody><row><entry align="center" valign="middle"><ptxt>Illuminates → Turns off</ptxt></entry><entry align="center" valign="middle"><ptxt>Ignition switch to ON → Engine is started</ptxt></entry><entry align="center" valign="middle"><judge-value label="1"><ptxt>A</ptxt></judge-value></entry></row><row><entry align="center" valign="middle"><ptxt>Other than above</ptxt></entry><entry align="center" valign="middle"><ptxt>-</ptxt></entry><entry align="center" valign="middle"><judge-value label="2"><ptxt>B (for LHD)</ptxt></judge-value></entry></row><row><entry align="center" valign="middle"><ptxt>Other than above</ptxt></entry><entry align="center" valign="middle"><ptxt>-</ptxt></entry><entry align="center" valign="middle"><judge-value label="3"><ptxt>B (for RHD)</ptxt></judge-value></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></spec></content6><results><result cellposition="1-1" label="1"><action actiontype="end" cellposition="2-1"><actiontitle>CHECK FOR INTERMITTENT PROBLEMS</actiontitle><content6><ptxt>Click here<mlink><xref href="RM100000000FJK6" label="Seep00001" term-id-from="001"/></mlink></ptxt></content6></action></result><result cellposition="1-2" label="2"><action actiontype="next" cellposition="2-2" childid="RM1000000017AMI_06_0003"/></result><result cellposition="1-6" label="3"><action actiontype="next" cellposition="2-6" childid="RM1000000017AMI_06_0010"/></result></results></testgrp><testgrp cellposition="2-2" id="RM1000000017AMI_06_0003"><testtitle>CHECK CONNECTION BETWEEN GTS AND ECM</testtitle><content6><test1><ptxt>Connect the GTS to the DLC3.</ptxt></test1><test1><ptxt>Turn the ignition switch to ON.</ptxt></test1><test1><ptxt>Turn the GTS on.</ptxt></test1><test1><ptxt>Check the communication between the GTS and ECM.</ptxt><atten4><ptxt>It can be checked using the "Engine" item of the Data List.</ptxt></atten4></test1><spec type="other"><title>Result</title><table pgwide="1"><tgroup cols="2"><colspec colname="col1" colwidth="3.51in"/><colspec colname="col2" colwidth="3.57in"/><thead><row><entry align="center" valign="middle"><ptxt>Result</ptxt></entry><entry align="center" valign="middle"><ptxt>Proceed to</ptxt></entry></row></thead><tbody><row><entry align="center" valign="middle"><ptxt>Communication is possible</ptxt></entry><entry align="center" valign="middle"><judge-value label="1"><ptxt>A</ptxt></judge-value></entry></row><row><entry align="center" valign="middle"><ptxt>Communication is not possible</ptxt></entry><entry align="center" valign="middle"><judge-value label="2"><ptxt>B</ptxt></judge-value></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></spec></content6><results><result cellposition="2-2" label="1"><action actiontype="next" cellposition="3-2" childid="RM1000000017AMI_06_0004"/></result><result cellposition="2-5" label="2"><action actiontype="end" cellposition="3-5"><actiontitle>GO TO VC OUTPUT CIRCUIT</actiontitle><content6><ptxt>Click here<mlink><xref href="RM1000000017AMF" label="Seep00001" term-id-from="004"/></mlink></ptxt></content6></action></result></results></testgrp><testgrp cellposition="3-2" id="RM1000000017AMI_06_0004"><testtitle>CHECK WHETHER DTC OUTPUT RECURS</testtitle><content6><test1><ptxt>Connect the GTS to the DLC3.</ptxt></test1><test1><ptxt>Turn the ignition switch to ON.</ptxt></test1><test1><ptxt>Turn the GTS on.</ptxt></test1><test1><ptxt>Enter the following menus: Powertrain / Engine and ECT / Trouble Codes.</ptxt><gts-info category="dtc-read"><title>Powertrain &gt; Engine and ECT &gt; Trouble Codes</title><gts-exec function-id="50001"><gts-ecu ecu-id="61"/></gts-exec><app-communication><app-param name="process-mode">0</app-param><app-param name="edit-mode">1</app-param><app-param name="insert-mode">0</app-param><app-param name="function-tab">0</app-param><app-param name="category-div">1</app-param><app-param name="category-div-name">Powertrain</app-param><app-param name="ecu-id">61</app-param><app-param name="ecu-name">Engine and ECT</app-param><app-param name="gts-order">0</app-param><app-param name="selected-state">0</app-param></app-communication></gts-info></test1><test1><ptxt>Check if any DTCs have been detected. Note down any DTCs.</ptxt></test1><spec type="other"><title>Result</title><table pgwide="1"><tgroup cols="2"><colspec colname="col1" colwidth="4.96in"/><colspec colname="col2" colwidth="2.12in"/><thead><row><entry align="center" valign="middle"><ptxt>Result</ptxt></entry><entry align="center" valign="middle"><ptxt>Proceed to</ptxt></entry></row></thead><tbody><row><entry align="center" valign="middle"><ptxt>DTCs are not output</ptxt></entry><entry align="center" valign="middle"><judge-value label="1"><ptxt>A</ptxt></judge-value></entry></row><row><entry align="center" valign="middle"><ptxt>Any DTCs is output</ptxt></entry><entry align="center" valign="middle"><judge-value label="2"><ptxt>B</ptxt></judge-value></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></spec><atten4><ptxt>Check for detected DTCs output from other ECUs which relate to the MIL.</ptxt></atten4></content6><results><result cellposition="3-2" label="1"><action actiontype="next" cellposition="4-2" childid="RM1000000017AMI_06_0005"/></result><result cellposition="3-4" label="2"><action actiontype="end" cellposition="4-4"><actiontitle>REPAIR CIRCUIT INDICATED BY OUTPUT DTC</actiontitle><content6/></action></result></results></testgrp><testgrp cellposition="4-2" id="RM1000000017AMI_06_0005"><testtitle>